# =============================================================================
# 01-auth.http — Testes de Autenticação
# =============================================================================
# Pré-requisito: copiar http-client.env.json para esta pasta
# No VS Code: instale "REST Client" (Humao) e clique em "Send Request"
# =============================================================================

### [1] Login Admin — deve retornar accessToken + refreshToken
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

### Após "Send Request" acima, copie o accessToken para adminToken no env.json

###

### [2] Login Admin com senha errada — deve retornar 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "SenhaErrada123!"
}

###

### [3] Login Admin com e-mail inexistente — deve retornar 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "naoexiste@teste.com",
  "password": "SenhaErrada123!"
}

###

### [4] Quick-Login de Cliente (sem mesa) — deve criar usuário + comanda
# @name quickLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/quick-login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Teste Automatizado",
  "cpf": "123.456.789-00",
  "whatsApp": "11999990001"
}

### Após "Send Request" acima, copie o accessToken para clientToken no env.json
### e o comandaId para comandaId no env.json

###

### [5] Quick-Login de Cliente com mesa — deve associar tableIdentifier
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/quick-login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Teste Mesa 5",
  "cpf": "111.222.333-44",
  "whatsApp": "11999990002",
  "tableIdentifier": "Mesa 5"
}

###

### [6] Refresh Token — deve retornar novo par de tokens
# Use o refreshToken retornado no loginAdmin (#1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "COLE_AQUI_O_REFRESH_TOKEN"
}

###

### [7] Logout — deve invalidar o refresh token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###
